    						<p class="card-text">Internationally, civil protection, police forces and emergency response agencies are under increasing pressure to more quickly and effectively respond to emergency situations. Moreover, such emergencies are common and recurring. For example, 50,000 people per-year on average die during natural disasters internationally. </p>
    						<!-- <a href="#" class="card-link">Card link</a>
